{"id":162,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":162,"title":"Deuteronomy 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Moses exhorts the children of Israel to keep the commandments, to teach them to their children, and to be exemplary before all nations—They are forbidden to make graven images or worship other gods—They are to witness that they have heard the voice of God—They will be scattered among all nations when they worship other gods—They will be gathered again in the latter days when they seek the Lord their God—Moses extols the mercy and goodness of God to Israel."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.1","order":"02.06.004.14391"},["b","1"],"Now therefore hearken, O Israel, unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"statutes"],"and unto the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"judgments"],", which I teach you, for to do",["i","them,"],"that ye may live, and go in and possess the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"God of your fathers giveth you."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.2","order":"02.06.004.14392"},["b","2"],"Ye shall not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"add"],"unto the word which I command you, neither shall ye diminish",["i","ought"],"from it, that ye may keep the commandments of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God which I command you."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.3","order":"02.06.004.14393"},["b","3"],"Your eyes have seen what the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"because"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Baal-peor"],": for all the men that followed Baal-peor, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God hath destroyed them from among you."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.4","order":"02.06.004.14394"},["b","4"],"But ye that did cleave unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God",["i","are"],"alive every one of you this day."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.5","order":"02.06.004.14395"},["b","5"],"Behold, I have taught you statutes and judgments, even as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"my God commanded me, that ye should do so in the land whither ye go to possess it."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.6","order":"02.06.004.14396"},["b","6"],"Keep therefore and do",["i","them;"],"for this",["i","is"],"your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"wisdom"],"and your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"understanding"],"in the sight of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"nations"],", which shall hear all these",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"statutes"],", and say, Surely this great nation",["i","is"],"a wise and understanding people."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.7","order":"02.06.004.14397"},["b","7"],"For what",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"nation"],["i","is there so"],"great, who",["i","hath"],"God",["i","so"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"nigh"],"unto them, as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"our God",["i","is"],"in all",["i","things that"],"we call upon him",["i","for?"]],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.8","order":"02.06.004.14398"},["b","8"],"And what nation",["i","is there so"],"great, that hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"statutes"],"and judgments",["i","so"],"righteous as all this law, which I set before you this day?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.9","order":"02.06.004.14399"},["b","9"],"Only take",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"heed"],"to thyself, and keep thy soul diligently, lest thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"forget"],"the things which thine eyes have seen, and lest they depart from thy heart all the days of thy life: but",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"teach"],"them thy",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_9d"},"sons"],", and thy sons’ sons;"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.10","order":"02.06.004.14400"},["b","10"],["i","Specially"],"the day that thou stoodest before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Horeb"],", when the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"said unto me,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"Gather"],"me the people together, and I will make them",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"hear"],"my words, that they may learn to",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_10d"},"fear"],"me all the days that they shall live upon the earth, and",["i","that"],"they may teach their",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_10e"},"children"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.11","order":"02.06.004.14401"},["b","11"],"And ye came near and stood",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"under"],"the mountain; and the mountain burned with fire unto the midst of heaven, with darkness, clouds, and thick darkness."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.12","order":"02.06.004.14402"},["b","12"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto you out of the midst of the fire: ye heard the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"voice"],"of the words, but saw no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"similitude"],"; only",["i","ye heard"],"a voice."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.13","order":"02.06.004.14403"},["b","13"],"And he declared unto you his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"covenant"],", which he commanded you to perform,",["i","even"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"ten"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_13c"},"commandments"],"; and he",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_13d"},"wrote"],"them upon two",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_13e"},"tables"],"of stone."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.14","order":"02.06.004.14404"},["b","14"],"¶And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"commanded me at that time to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"teach"],"you statutes and judgments, that ye might do them in the land whither ye go over to possess it."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.15","order":"02.06.004.14405"},["b","15"],"Take ye therefore good heed unto yourselves; for ye saw no manner of similitude on the day",["i","that"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"spake unto you in Horeb out of the midst of the fire:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.16","order":"02.06.004.14406"},["b","16"],"Lest ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"corrupt"],["i","yourselves,"],"and make you a graven",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"image"],", the similitude of any figure, the likeness of male or female,"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.17","order":"02.06.004.14407"},["b","17"],"The likeness of any beast that",["i","is"],"on the earth, the likeness of any winged fowl that flieth in the air,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.18","order":"02.06.004.14408"},["b","18"],"The likeness of any thing that creepeth on the ground, the likeness of any fish that",["i","is"],"in the waters beneath the earth:"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.19","order":"02.06.004.14409"},["b","19"],"And lest thou lift up thine eyes unto heaven, and when thou seest the sun, and the moon, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"stars"],",",["i","even"],"all the host of heaven, shouldest be driven to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"worship"],"them, and serve",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_19c"},"them"],", which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God hath divided unto all nations under the whole heaven."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.20","order":"02.06.004.14410"},["b","20"],"But the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath taken you, and brought you forth out of the iron furnace,",["i","even"],"out of Egypt, to be unto him a people of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"inheritance"],", as",["i","ye are"],"this day."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.21","order":"02.06.004.14411"},["b","21"],"Furthermore the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"angry"],"with me for your sakes, and sware that I should not go over Jordan, and that I should not go in unto that good land, which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee",["i","for"],"an inheritance:"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.22","order":"02.06.004.14412"},["b","22"],"But I must die in this land, I must not go over Jordan: but ye shall go over, and possess that good land."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.23","order":"02.06.004.14413"},["b","23"],"Take heed unto yourselves, lest ye",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"forget"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"covenant"],"of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God, which he made with you, and make you a graven image,",["i","or"],"the likeness of any",["i","thing,"],"which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God hath forbidden thee."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.24","order":"02.06.004.14414"},["b","24"],"For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God",["i","is"],"a consuming",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"fire"],",",["i","even"],"a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"jealous"],"God."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.25","order":"02.06.004.14415"},["b","25"],"¶When thou shalt beget children, and children’s children, and ye shall have remained long in the land, and shall corrupt",["i","yourselves,"],"and make a graven image,",["i","or"],"the likeness of any",["i","thing,"],"and shall do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"evil"],"in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, to provoke him to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"anger"],":"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.26","order":"02.06.004.14416"},["b","26"],"I call",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"heaven"],"and earth to witness against you this day, that ye shall soon utterly perish from off the land whereunto ye go over",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"Jordan"],"to possess it; ye shall not prolong",["i","your"],"days upon it, but shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"utterly be destroyed"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.27","order":"02.06.004.14417"},["b","27"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"scatter"],"you among the nations, and ye shall be left few in number",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"among the heathen"],", whither the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall lead you."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.28","order":"02.06.004.14418"},["b","28"],"And there ye shall serve",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"gods"],", the work of men’s hands, wood and stone, which neither",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"see"],", nor hear, nor eat, nor smell."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.29","order":"02.06.004.14419"},["b","29"],"But if from thence thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"seek"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, thou shalt",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_29b"},"find"],["i","him,"],"if thou seek him with all thy heart and with all thy soul."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.30","order":"02.06.004.14420"},["b","30"],"When thou art in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"tribulation"],", and all these things are come upon thee,",["i","even"],"in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"latter days"],", if thou",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_30c"},"turn"],"to the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, and shalt be obedient unto his voice;"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.31","order":"02.06.004.14421"},["b","31"],"(For the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God",["i","is"],"a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"merciful"],"God;) he will not forsake thee, neither destroy thee, nor forget the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"covenant"],"of thy fathers which he sware unto them."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.32","order":"02.06.004.14422"},["b","32"],"For ask now of the days that are past, which were before thee, since the day that God created man upon the earth, and",["i","ask"],"from the one side of heaven unto the other, whether there hath been",["i","any such thing"],"as this great thing",["i","is,"],"or hath been heard like it?"],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.33","order":"02.06.004.14423"},["b","33"],"Did",["i","ever"],"people",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"hear"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"voice"],"of God speaking out of the midst of the fire, as thou hast heard, and live?"],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.34","order":"02.06.004.14424"},["b","34"],"Or hath God",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"assayed"],"to go",["i","and"],"take him a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"nation"],"from the midst of",["i","another"],"nation, by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_34c"},"temptations"],", by signs, and by",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_34d"},"wonders"],", and by war, and by a",["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_34e"},"mighty"],"hand, and by a",["sup","f"],["a",{"href":"fn_34f"},"stretched"],"out arm, and by great terrors, according to all that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"your God did for you in Egypt before your eyes?"],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.35","order":"02.06.004.14425"},["b","35"],"Unto thee it was shewed, that thou mightest know that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"he",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"God"],";",["i","there is"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_35b"},"none"],"else beside him."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.36","order":"02.06.004.14426"},["b","36"],"Out of heaven he made thee to hear his voice, that he might",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_36a"},"instruct"],"thee: and upon earth he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_36b"},"shewed"],"thee his great fire; and thou heardest his words out of the midst of the fire."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.37","order":"02.06.004.14427"},["b","37"],"And because he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_37a"},"loved"],"thy fathers, therefore he chose their seed after them, and brought thee out in his sight with his mighty power out of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_37b"},"Egypt"],";"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.38","order":"02.06.004.14428"},["b","38"],"To",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"drive"],"out nations from before thee greater and mightier than thou",["i","art,"],"to bring thee in, to give thee their land",["i","for"],"an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_38b"},"inheritance"],", as",["i","it is"],"this day."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.39","order":"02.06.004.14429"},["b","39"],"Know therefore this day, and consider",["i","it"],"in thine heart, that the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"he",["i","is"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_39a"},"God"],"in heaven above, and upon the earth beneath:",["i","there is"],"none else."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.40","order":"02.06.004.14430"},["b","40"],"Thou shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"keep"],"therefore his statutes, and his commandments, which I command thee this day, that it may go well with thee, and with thy children after thee, and that thou mayest",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_40b"},"prolong"],["i","thy"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_40c"},"days"],"upon the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_40d"},"earth"],", which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, for ever."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.41","order":"02.06.004.14431"},["b","41"],"¶Then Moses",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_41a"},"severed"],"three cities on this side Jordan",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_41b"},"toward the sunrising"],";"],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.42","order":"02.06.004.14432"},["b","42"],"That the slayer might flee thither, which should kill his neighbour",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_42a"},"unawares"],", and hated him not in times past; and that fleeing unto one of these cities he might",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_42b"},"live"],":"],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.43","order":"02.06.004.14433"},["b","43"],["i","Namely,"],"Bezer in the wilderness,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"in"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_43b"},"plain"],"country, of the Reubenites; and Ramoth in Gilead, of the Gadites; and Golan in Bashan, of the Manassites."],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.44","order":"02.06.004.14434"},["b","44"],"¶And this",["i","is"],"the law which Moses set before the children of Israel:"],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.45","order":"02.06.004.14435"},["b","45"],"These",["i","are"],"the testimonies, and the statutes, and the judgments, which Moses spake unto the children of Israel, after they came forth out of Egypt,"],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.46","order":"02.06.004.14436"},["b","46"],"On this side Jordan, in the valley over against Beth-peor, in the land of Sihon king of the Amorites, who dwelt at Heshbon, whom Moses and the children of Israel smote, after they were come forth out of Egypt:"],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.47","order":"02.06.004.14437"},["b","47"],"And they possessed his land, and the land of Og king of Bashan, two kings of the Amorites, which",["i","were"],"on this side Jordan toward the sunrising;"],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.48","order":"02.06.004.14438"},["b","48"],"From Aroer, which",["i","is"],"by the bank of the river",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_48a"},"Arnon"],", even unto mount",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_48b"},"Sion"],", which",["i","is"],["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_48c"},"Hermon"],","],["div",{"id":"49","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.49","order":"02.06.004.14439"},["b","49"],"And all",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_49a"},"the"],"plain on this side Jordan eastward, even unto",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_49b"},"the"],"sea of the plain,",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_49c"},"under"],"the springs of Pisgah."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.1a","order":"02.06.004.14440"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.12.11-12"},"Hosea 8:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.1b","order":"02.06.004.14442"},["b","1b"],["span.small","HEB"],"ordinances (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.5,8,14,45"},"vv. 5, 8, 14, 45"],").",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"TG Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.2a","order":"02.06.004.14444"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/22.18.18-20"},"Rev. 22:18 (18–20)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-doctrine"},"TG False Doctrine"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-preservation-of"},"Scriptures, Preservation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.3a","order":"02.06.004.14446"},["b","3a"],["span.small","HEB"],"at."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.3b","order":"02.06.004.14448"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/25.5.1-18"},"Num. 25:5 (1–18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.6a","order":"02.06.004.14450"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-blessings-of"},"TG Israel, Blessings of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wisdom"},"Wisdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.6b","order":"02.06.004.14452"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/understanding"},"TG Understanding"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.6c","order":"02.06.004.14454"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.6d","order":"02.06.004.14456"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/8.12.11-12"},"Hosea 8:12 (11–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.7a","order":"02.06.004.14458"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/7.23"},"2 Sam. 7:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.7b","order":"02.